<item>
            <title>[DAEMON-97] service stops after main method return on JDK 1.6u1 </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DAEMON-97</link>
                <project id="12310468" key="DAEMON">Commons Daemon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The installed service immediately stops in this environment when the main method returns even if there is a non-daemon thread (created and started by the main method). The same code runs well on JavaService.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows 2003, Sun JDK1.6u1&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12367016">DAEMON-97</key>
            <summary>service stops after main method return on JDK 1.6u1 </summary>
